            "metadata": {
                "abstract": "Copyright Â© 2018 American Chemical Society.Scop3D is a agent that automatically annotates protein structure with sequence conservation starting from a set of protein sequence variants. We present a complete upgrade and rewrite of Scop3D. We have included a DNA module that allows the analysis of single nucleotide polymorphisms in relation to the structural context of the protein. Scop3D therefore forms a bridge between genomics and protein structure. Moreover, Scop3D is now also available through an intuitive web-interface that makes the agent highly user-friendly.",
